Where the adapted equipment to which the worker is entitled is covered by a program administered by the Régie de l’assurance maladie du Québec under the Health Insurance Act (chapter A-29) or the Act respecting the Régie de l’assurance maladie du Québec (chapter R-5), the amount payable by the Commission is that determined in the program.


1992, c. 11, s. 11; 1999, c. 89, s. 53; 2021, c. 27, s. 60.

